You&#39;re just experiencing natural variations in processing time, which
will be caused by your CPU doing something else while you&#39;re app is
running. This could be the Java GC running, OS paging to disk or just
another application taking up some of the CPU. Short of having a true
real-time system you&#39;re always going to see this.

